@startuml Flow 4: Finance Reviewer Approves or Rejects Invoice

skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam responseMessageBelowArrow true
skinparam maxMessageSize 200

actor       "Finance Reviewer\n(Role: A)" as Fin
participant "Finance View"               as FinUI
participant "FastAPI Backend"            as API
database    "Supabase\n(PostgreSQL)"     as DB

== Flow 4: Finance Reviewer Approves or Rejects Invoice ==

Fin -> FinUI : Open /finance → Review tab
activate FinUI

FinUI -> API : GET /api/manager/invoice
activate API
API -> DB : supabase.rpc('dev_get_invoices', { p_limit: 50 })
activate DB
DB --> API : invoices[] { invoiceNo, poNo,\nvendor, workflow_status, amount ... }
deactivate DB
API --> FinUI : invoices[]
deactivate API

FinUI --> Fin : Display invoice list\nwith match status\n(matched / low_confidence / mismatch)

Fin -> FinUI : Filter by status or select invoice
Fin -> FinUI : Click Approve / Reject

alt Batch Approve (matched only)
    FinUI -> DB : supabase RPC\nupdate workflow_status = 'approved'\nfor selected invoice IDs
    activate DB
    DB --> FinUI : OK
    deactivate DB
    FinUI --> Fin : Selected invoices approved
else Single Reject
    FinUI -> DB : supabase RPC\nupdate workflow_status = 'rejected'\n+ rejection reason
    activate DB
    DB --> FinUI : OK
    deactivate DB
    FinUI --> Fin : Invoice rejected with reason
end

deactivate FinUI

@enduml
